               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gospel of Luke (fols.1-17rb), incomplete
 - Bǝsrāta Luqās “Gospel
                     of Luke” (fols. 1-17rb), incomplete
 - Short postscript (fol. 17rb)
                     II) Gospel of John (17v-31v), incomplete
 - Bǝsrāta Yoḥannǝs "Gospel of
                     John" (17v-31v)
 III) Gospel of Matthew (fols. 32r-69r), incomplete
                     Bǝsrāta Mātewos "Gospel of Matthew" (32r-69r)
 - Short postscript (fol.
                     69r) 
 IV) Gospel of Mark (fols. 69v-109v)
 - List of the "tituli" for
                     the Gospel of Mark, 27 titles (fol. 69v)
 - Bǝsrāta Mārqos "Gospel of Mark"
                     (fols. 70r-109v)
 - Short postscript (fol. 109vb).</summary>
